data.name: CustomSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT Emp.code,emp.CompanyID,Department.DivId,emp.DeptId,emp.Position,emp.GroupId,emp.WageType,emp.Contractor, RPT_EmpWork.DayOfWeek, RPT_EmpWork.DateIn, RPT_EmpWork.Time1, RPT_EmpWork.Time2, RPT_EmpWork.Time3, RPT_EmpWork.Time4, RPT_EmpWork.DayDo, DayDo_str = case when isnull(RPT_EmpWork.DayDo,0) = 1 then '1(0.0)' when isnull(RPT_EmpWork.DayDo,0) = 0.5 then '0(0.4)' else '0(' + convert(nvarchar(10),convert(numeric(9,1),isnull(RPT_EmpWork.DayDo,0))) + ')' end, RPT_EmpWork.OT1, RPT_EmpWork.OT15, RPT_EmpWork.OT2, RPT_EmpWork.OT3, RPT_EmpWork.Val, RPT_EmpWork.Absent, Absent_str = case when isnull(RPT_EmpWork.Absent,0) <> 0 then 'ขาด' else '' end, RPT_EmpWork.Late, RPT_EmpWork.LateOT, RPT_EmpWork.WorkTime, RPT_EmpWork.Code, Division.Division, Department.Department, Emp.Title, Emp.Fname, Emp.Lname, RPT_EmpWork.KaCode as KaCode, isnull(TimeKa.KaName,'') as KaName, RPT_EmpWork.CardForget, CardForget_str = case when isnull(RPT_EmpWork.CardForget,0) = 0 then '' else 'M' end, RPT_EmpWork.Holiday, isnull(RPT_EmpWork.valCode,'') as valCode, isnull(RPT_EmpWork.Vacation,'') as Vacation, Company_Sub.CompanyName, TotalLate = isnull(RPT_EmpWork.Late,0) + isnull(RPT_EmpWork.LateOT,0) FROM (((RPT_EmpWork RPT_EmpWork LEFT OUTER JOIN Emp Emp ON RPT_EmpWork.Code=Emp.Code) LEFT OUTER JOIN Department Department ON Emp.DeptId=Department.DeptId) LEFT OUTER JOIN Division Division ON Department .DivId=Division.DivId) LEFT OUTER JOIN Company_Sub Company_Sub ON Emp.CompanyID=Company_Sub.CompanyID left outer join TimeKa TimeKa on RPT_EmpWork.Kacode = TimeKa.Ka_code ORDER BY RPT_EmpWork.Code, RPT_EmpWork.DateIn
